ui/

Owns: Screens and user interaction:

Start/Load, Party Creator, Inventory, Town, Combat view

Button handlers & keyboard/touch bindings

Subscribes to events and renders panels
Exposes: None (entry points only).
Depends on: core (events), gameplay domains (read/query/commands).
Must not be imported by: any non-UI code.
Why: Presentation separated from rules, easier to reskin.